		<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p>This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information.</p>

		<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
		<p>We may collect personal information from you such as your name, email address, mailing address, phone number, or credit card information when you use our services, make a purchase, or interact with our website.</p>

